nodes.text: The Naboo delegation was a group of diplomats that represented the planet of Naboo in the Senate of the Galactic Republic. Senator Sheev Palpatine served as head of the delegation during his tenure as the Naboo's representative in the waning years of the Republic. With Palpatine's election to the office of Supreme Chancellor, his former post was eventually attained by Padmé Amidala following her reign as Queen of Naboo.
